title: fanoutqa: Who were the principals of the main artists' high schools in the two songs that Bryson Tiller made guest appearances on in 2022? (ddb5f93339663076)

chat_history.content: Who were the principals of the main artists' high schools in the two songs that Bryson Tiller made guest appearances on in 2022?

I couldn't find any songs that Bryson Tiller made guest appearances on in 2022. In 2021, he appeared on the song 'Keep Calm' by RJMrLA, and in 2020 he appeared on 'Always Been' by Ty Dolla Sign.

Would you like to know more about either of these songs?
